# project-values-all

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `column_pruning_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (project ?cols (values ?rows))
rhs: (values ?rows)
